    • Method Detail

      • getID

        int getID()
        Get token ID.

        The token ID is compiler-specific value. Each token must have unique ID.

        Returns:
        ID of the token

      • getType

        int getType()
        Get token type.

        The token type mus be one of the pre-defined constants located inside this interface (e.g. RESERVED, PREPROCESSOR, etc.).

        Returns:
        type of the token
